---

<Layout title="Johnny Watts Agency — Your Trusted Insurance Specialists">

  <!-- ═══ HERO — gradient bg, text LEFT, circular image RIGHT ═══ -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden text-white" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3757e1 0%, #00b4d8 50%, #7b2ff7 100%);">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-16 md:py-24">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-white mb-4" style="font-size:2.5rem; line-height:1.15;">We Are Your Trusted Specialists</h1>
          <p class="text-white/90 mb-6" style="font-size:1rem; line-height:1.7;">
            We are your Medicare, Health Insurance Marketplace, and Life Insurance specialists. Our decades of combined experience are at your service to ensure that you will get the best options for your needs.
          </p>
          <a href="/about/" class="btn">About Us</a>
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-center">
          <div class="w-72 h-72 md:w-96 md:h-96 rounded-full overflow-hidden border-4 border-white/30 shadow-2xl">
            <img
              src="https://cdn.sanity.io/images/ssbenczy/production/0ea061d233b07bc91d306af7b3615e7d9bba7875-2560x1707.jpg?w=800&h=800&fit=crop&auto=format"
              alt="Happy family"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
              loading="eager"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Wave bottom -->
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full overflow-hidden leading-none">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 1440 120" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-full h-16 md:h-24">
        <path d="M0,80 C360,120 720,40 1440,80 L1440,120 L0,120 Z" fill="#ffffff"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ WHY CHOOSE — image LEFT circle, text RIGHT ═══ -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 relative">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <!-- Circular image with decorative ring -->
        <div class="flex justify-center">
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="w-64 h-64 md:w-80 md:h-80 rounded-full overflow-hidden shadow-xl">
              <img
                src="https://cdn.sanity.io/images/ssbenczy/production/17f6656e1958d23ff03f1d52889993476f1cb7e0-1024x683.jpg?w=640&h=640&fit=crop&auto=format"
                alt="Couple planning insurance"
                class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                loading="lazy"
              />
            </div>
            <!-- Decorative curved line -->
            <div class="absolute -bottom-8 -left-8 w-32 h-32 border-4 border-primary/20 rounded-full"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Text -->
        <div>
          <p class="kicker">Your Health, Your Future, Your Family, Your Peace Of Mind</p>
          <h2 class="mb-4">Why Choose Johnny Watts Agency?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray leading-relaxed mb-6">
            We specialize in providing Medicare, Health Insurance, and Life Insurance services. We know that decisions concerning these are not to be taken lightly and that's why we take the time to understand your needs and we're here to guide you through the process with expertise and dedication. You might ask, "How are you different?" Good question. As a recruiter, I help Medicare and insurance agents all across America find the best companies to recommend to their clients. As your local agent, I'll access over 40 top insurance companies and compare their rates for the plan that fits you best. In addition, my platform is a top-tier health insurance marketplace that offers services tailored to your needs.
          </p>
          <a href="/about/" class="btn">Learn More</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Decorative curve -->
    <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -left-16 w-64 h-64 border-4 border-primary/10 rounded-full hidden md:block"></div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ COMPANY AFFILIATION / OUR PARTNERS ═══ -->
